blogs.title: Ego is the Enemy
blogs.author: Ryan Holiday
blogs.body: Ego Is the Enemy is the fourth book by author Ryan Holiday, published on June 14, 2016. It is about the treacherous nature of ego.

blogs.title: Blacklist
blogs.author: Raymond Redington
blogs.body: A wanted fugitive mysteriously surrenders himself to the FBI and offers to help them capture deadly criminals. His sole condition is that he will work only with the new profiler, Elizabeth Keen.
